comments: RLB shows Towns (MIN) gets his arm across the ball and ties it up as Portis (WAS) gathers in the lane.
Teague (MIN) makes marginal contact with Satoransky (WAS) during the loose ball.
Towns (MIN) holds Portis' (WAS) arm during the rebound and affects his ability to gather the loose ball.
Beal (WAS) establishes himself in a screening position in Teague's (MIN) path and does not deliver the contact.
Towns (MIN) engages with Portis (WAS) as the shot is released, but does not affect his ability to get to the rebound.
Towns (MIN) maintains legal guarding position during Ariza's (WAS) drive and does not deliver contact that affects his ability to pass.
Rose (MIN) makes marginal contact with Ariza (WAS) during the drive.
